            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "My experience with the office staff and others have been very good. All my queries were patiently and properly handled. They  are much more well behaved than many schools around. Was happy to see how parents are treated. Impressed by the infrastructure.",
          "publisher": {
