          "reviewBody": "This year they directly increased fees by 12-15k ..its too much..as per their standard fees are very high and staff are not upto the mark...principal and staff doesnt have a knowladge. They just behind to complete curriculum. Principal only interested in makeup and talk in English, she doesnt have knowladge to how to run the school, how to handle students,  staff and parents also.. I never came across such a worst principal ever. If u as a parent go there with some issue..they target you as parents as well they target student also. I complained again one of the teacher but they target my kid . They don't want to resolve issue  but they Created mess and my kid sufferedstill suffering...next year definitely I will change the school.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
