          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "4",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "It is one of the best co-educational English medium CBSE Board School in Balewadi, Pune. My granddaughter is studying in this school. The school has good infrastructure, Lab, Computer class, Library, Indoor games & playground. The school has experienced & caring team of teachers and the principal is very attentive, vigilant and passionate to students. For a diligent, attentive and honest student, the infrastructure of the school is not more important than its efficient and sincere teachers. My granddaughter and we are overall satisfied with this institute.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
